@dpsBase = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@authToken = user_token_123

### Contexto del grafo para RAG (a partir de una pregunta)
POST {{dpsBase}}/graph/context
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "question": "¿Qué organismos regulan la aviación civil?",
  "chat_id": 1,
  "max_entities": 8,
  "max_relations": 30
}


### Contexto del grafo a partir de términos
POST {{dpsBase}}/graph/context
Accept: application/json
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "terms": ["aviación civil", "aeródromo"],
  "max_entities": 10,
  "max_relations": 40
}
